setUp().notice: Setup deploys the DIDManager and TestCredentialManager and registers a test DID.

testValidateActiveCredential().notice: Tests that an active, properly signed credential validates correctly.

testValidateCredentialWithInvalidSignatu.notice: Tests that a credential signed with an invalid signature reverts with "Recovered signer mismatch".

testValidateExpiredCredential().notice: Tests that an expired credential reverts with the CredentialExpired error.

testValidateRevokedCredential().notice: Tests that a revoked credential reverts with "Credential has been revoked".

testValidateUnsignedCredential().notice: Tests that a credential that has not been signed reverts with "Credential is not signed".
